            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName>Bonitio qui Bonodie vocor</persName> filio bone memorie
                            <persName>Teutii</persName> vende in <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        que est <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/126">Sancti
                            Bartholomei</orgName> apostoli qui ponitur in <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/281">Sestinge</placeName> et vocitatur
                            <placeName ref="#places/281">Curte Maiberti</placeName>, et in <persName
                            key="#Abbots">Andrea</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abb(ate)</rs> et in omnes suos successores (…) integra mea
                        portione de <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> qui est pos(ita) intro
                            <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/154">Rosellensi</geogName>
                        <placeName key="#Curtes"><geogName key="#Mountains #Curtes #Carbonaria"><rs
                                    key="#Curtes">Curte</rs> Sancti Fridiani</geogName></placeName>
                        cum omni sua pertinentia, essepto et antepono summitate de <rs
                            key="#Mountains #Defensive_elements">monte</rs> infra <rs
                            key="#Carbonaria">carbonaria</rs> permanente; ipsa terra posita est in
                            <placeName key="#Mountains #Landed_possessions #Carbonaria"
                            ref="#places/281">Sestinge</placeName> prope predicto monasterio Sancti
                        Bartholomei, sicut mihi per <rs key="#Venditio">chartula comparationis</rs>
                        evenit da <persName>Raineri</persName> et <persName>Fralmi</persName>
                        germani filiorum bone memorie <persName>Alberici qui Albitio</persName>
                        vocabatur; prezzo argentum mensuratos solidos quadraginta. Chiede a
                            <persName key="#Notary #Judge">Romano</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> domni
                        imperatoris la stesura della cartula. Actum ante <orgName
                            key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/125"><rs
                                key="#Baptismal_churches">plebe</rs> de <placeName
                                key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#places/274"
                            >Morrano</placeName></orgName>. Testimoni: <persName>Girardi</persName>
                        filii <persName>Conradi</persName>; <persName>Ilditii</persName> filii bone
                        memorie <persName>Roitii</persName>; Pepi filii bone memorie
                            <persName>Rateri</persName>. <persName>Autori: + Bonizio detto Bonodie
                            del fu Teuzio, Andrea abbas. Scrittore: Romano notarius et iudex dom.
                            imp. Testimoni sottoscrittori: + Gherardo di Corrado, + Ildizio del fu
                            Rozio, + Pepo del fu Raterio. Altro: gg. Ranieri e Fraolmi del fu
                            Alberico detto Albizio.</persName>
                        <placeName>Morrano (La Pieve, Scarlino), Sestinge, Curte Maiberti (Badia
                            Vecchia, Castiglione della Pescaia), Curte Sancti Fridiani (Il Convento,
                            Castiglione della Pescaia), Rusellae (Bagno Roselle,
                            Grosseto).</placeName>
                        <orgName>San Bartolomeo di Sestinga, San Donato di Morrano (chiesa
                            battesimale).</orgName>
                    </ab>
